When I select 'Perifocal edema' checkbox 
Then checkbox is checked
When I select 'Abscess' checkbox 
Then 'Max. Diameter' input field is enabled 

When I enter '1' in the 'Max. Diameter' input field
Then the number is accepted 
When I enter '99' in the 'Max. Diameter' input field
Then the number is accepted 

When I select 'Midline shift' checkbox
Then 'To the right' radio button is enabled
And 'To the left' radio button is enabled
And 'Extent of midline shift' input field is enabled 

When I select 'To the right' radio button
Then radio button is selected
When I select 'To the left' radio button
Then radio button is selected

When I enter '1' in the 'Extent of midline shift' input field
Then the number is accepted 
When I enter '99' in the 'Extent of midline shift' input field
Then the number is accepted 

When I select 'Involvement of ventricles' checkbox
Then 'Lateral ventricle right' checkbox is enabled 
And 'Lateral ventricle left' checkbox is enabled
And '3rd ventricle' checkbox is enabled

When I select 'No' radio button
Then radio button is selected

When I select 'Low' radio button 
Then 'Homogenous' radio button is enabled 
And 'Heterogeneous' radio button is enabled 
And 'Peripheral' radio button is enabled 
And 'Ring-shaped' radio button is enabled 
And 'Entire lesion' radio button is enabled 
And 'Central' radio button is enabled 
And 'Septal' radio button is enabled 

